<s-1 id="RM0000026TQ001X_01_0011" proc-id="RM0250U___00006H500000">
<ptxt>INSPECT CRANKSHAFT BEARING CAP SET BOLT</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using vernier calipers, measure the tension portion diameter of the bolts.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A064458" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Standard diameter</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>7.3 to 7.5 mm (0.287 to 0.295 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<spec>
<title>Minimum diameter</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>7.2 mm (0.284 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the diameter is less than the minimum, replace the bolt.</ptxt>
</s2>
